modules.description: This module implements pipelines that process ordered input data through synchronous and asynchronous transformations, handling both successful and error-bearing results. It supports operations like serial and parallel async steps, error mapping, result extraction, and key-based tracking, working with lists and result-wrapped values. Concrete use cases include processing HTTP requests with mixed success/failure outcomes, transforming streams of keyed records, and aggregating pipeline results into maps or error groups.
